- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is another possible category as the paper may involve processing sensor data from cameras or other visual sensors. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper may involve using machine learning techniques to analyze and classify sensor data. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may involve designing control systems for mobile robots based on the topological maps.
